<refsect1 id="GdvTwodLayer.description" role="desc">
<title role="desc.title">Description</title>
<para>GdvTowdLayer plots an usual cartesian XY-style graph. It handles GdvAxis- and
GdvLayerContent-Objects.</para>

</refsect1>
